snippet.title: Out Run - Atari ST (1987)
snippet.description:
"Out Run" is a racing game released for Atari ST in 1987 and developed by Probe.

01:02 Stage 1
02:15 Stage 2
03:21 Game Over
03:30 Stage 1
04:50 Stage 2
05:54 Game Over
06:05 Stage 1
07:08 Stage 2
08:12 Stage 3
09:22 Game Over

Conversion of the famous arcade game from Sega, this is a game that I found unfortunately quite unplayable. There are a lot of better racing games on Atari ST.
